        "text": "<p><strong>About 64 South Street</strong></p><p>Visit our showroom at 64 South Street to meet our renowned experts and enjoy a private consultation.<br/><br/>Our Boutique & Showroom is open Tuesday to Saturday and by appointment.</p>",
