            "grid_image_size": "square",
            "heading": "Sourcing Gemstones",
            "text": "<p>We pride ourselves on sourcing the most brilliant, ethically sourced diamonds and coloured gemstones. As GIA-qualified specialists, we navigate the global market to find stones that offer true beauty and value.</p><p>We work strictly with suppliers who adhere to the Kimberley Process, ensuring conflict-free origins, and we also offer a stunning selection of high-quality lab-grown diamonds for our environmentally conscious clients.</p>",
            "button_link": "shopify://pages/bespoke-jewellery-designs",
            "button_text": "Go to Bespoke Design"
