        "image_and_text_4whJQy": {
          "type": "image_and_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/hammer.svg",
            "grid_image_size": "square",
            "heading": "Casting & Metals",
            "text": "<p>The foundation of fine jewellery lies in the quality of its metal. We work exclusively with high-grade Platinum and 18ct Gold. Our commitment to sustainability means we prioritise the use of 100% recycled precious metals in our bespoke creations.</p><p>Furthermore, our<a href=\"/pages/jewellery-remodelling-service\" title=\"Jewellery Remodelling Service\"> remodelling service</a> allows us to melt down your unworn, sentimental family gold to forge entirely new, modern designs, keeping the history alive while reducing environmental impact.</p>",
            "button_link": "shopify://pages/jewellery-remodelling-service",
            "button_text": "Go to Remodelling"
          }
        },
