          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/sparkles.svg",
            "grid_image_size": "square",
            "heading": "Setting, Polishing & Repairs",
            "text": "<p>All of our centre stone setting, resizing and <a href=\"/blogs/guide-jewellery-repair-service/jewellery-repair-service\" title=\"Jewellery Repair Service Guide\">repairs </a>are done by our trusted gemstone setters.</p><p>Our skilled craftspeople restore damaged, worn, or cherished pieces to their original beauty.<br/><br/>Expert care including ring resizing, claw retipping, cleaning, and chain soldering.</p>",
            "button_link": "shopify://pages/jewellery-repair-service",
